{"tid":1027011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[往死裡打]連登女神謝安琪個仔居然學人「走塑」!!!!","createTime":"2019-02-18T13:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T13:08:21.000Z","uid":27064,"like":7,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2824fe2fcbb7778943eb7e732c09d8558dcc3e41","tid":1027011,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"圈中數一數二嘅愛妻號張繼聰，唔只成日出招冧老婆謝安琪，就連小朋友都教得好好！現年11歲嘅大仔張瞻尋日去幫全家幫珍珠奶茶（珍奶），重點係佢竟然自攜水樽去買，響應「走塑」，支持環保！佢喺Instagram上載咗段片，見佢將一樽樽珍珠奶茶放入環保袋，驟眼睇已經有4樽，雖然都唔輕，但佢堅持自己拎同放，最後佢仲用勁溫柔嘅聲線同店員講：「唔該晒！」店員姐姐都畀佢冧暈同佢揮手Bye Bye！<br />\n<br />\n而阿聰都轉發片段同讚「乖」，唔少網民激讚「好家教」、「好叻豬」、「好生性～好鍾意你對仔女」，仲有人笑言等佢長大要嫁畀佢咁話！而育有4個仔女嘅林盛斌（Bob）都忍唔住留言讚：「有料👍」呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190218/photo/bkn-20190218180208992-0218_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190218193040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190218180208992-0218_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190218193040&h=83bdd54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190218/photo/bkn-20190218180208992-0218_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190218193040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190218180208992-0218_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190218193040&h=0298b06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢竟然帶私家樽去買，仲自己一手一腳裝同拎！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔一手一腳捧紅嘅謝安琪<br />\n明知連登仔反環保 反「走塑」都專登咁教個仔<br />\n擺明落你哋面姐</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d5f55409957cf3ebf4f116fb27fc09455394e","tid":1027011,"uid":24457,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"2e5fdea752a5396f0017d61b89b1a6946866f36c","tid":1027011,"uid":171594,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"呢種走法唔會屌<br />\n起碼唔會煩到人<br />\n係咪真係環保就另計"},{"pid":"854d21386a79394ba5b359cceb4d16167ff66186","tid":1027011,"uid":197644,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/f0quefU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0quefU.png&h=cabac7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叻仔，錫啖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSK28ui1CRz3HrnRC8GOHXu8pLs3biD4NodmwqKjh8ItqUErtxe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSK28ui1CRz3HrnRC8GOHXu8pLs3biD4NodmwqKjh8ItqUErtxe&h=a375c6b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4880d639d09c3f8bf2b2829b1da9e13568ecc161","tid":1027011,"uid":56610,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"環保同環保撚係兩樣野黎"},{"pid":"b97e6985b958a818db80e0dd9fcdd698ff802b07","tid":1027011,"uid":221150,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"環保真係冇問題，個人自由，但環保撚係強迫人地跟佢個套，唔比人揀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677de90a8d6f8ad64091eb051f0ee3aca943993f","tid":1027011,"uid":43823,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"佢個仔又唔係指住其他買珍珠奶茶嘅人屌佢地做乜唔自備樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d66a775d0de258740bb332105fc20e8de5d5149","tid":1027011,"uid"